cloudflare-register is a smart Dynamic DNS service for Cloudflare.

It manages multiple hostnames across multiple Cloudflare zones, supports
dual-stack (IPv4 + IPv6) with auto-detection and state synchronization, and
exposes a JWT-protected web UI plus a Textual-based TUI dashboard for
keyboard-driven operation. A cron-friendly `sync --once` mode lets the
service run on hosts without a system service supervisor.
